OL,3,CCardiff University to scale down music
OL,4,Cand languages degrees but scrap others
OL,6,FCardiff University has announced it
OL,7,Fplans to close its ancient history and
OL,8,Freligion and theology degrees, and
OL,9,Fscale down its music and modern
OL,10,Flanguages courses.
OL,12,FThe university announced plans to make
OL,13,F400 staff ` around 7% of the workforce
OL,14,F` redundant and reduce a number of
OL,15,Fdegree courses, initially including
OL,16,Fnursing, in January, with that number
OL,17,Fthen reduced to a proposed 286 in
OL,18,FApril, after a number of staff had
OL,19,Falready opted for voluntary redundancy.
