OL,3,CCardiff University to scale down music
OL,4,Cand languages degrees but scrap others
OL,6,FIn an update sent to staff on Tuesday,
OL,7,FCardiff University's vice-chancellor,
OL,8,FProfessor Wendy Larner, said it now
OL,9,Fproposes to retain its offerings of
OL,10,Fmodern languages and music research
OL,11,Fand education but with revised
OL,12,Fstructures and a smaller staff base,
OL,13,Fwithin a new School of Global
OL,14,FHumanities.
