OL,3,CCardiff University to scale down music
OL,4,Cand languages degrees but scrap others
OL,6,FProfessor Larner said: "Having
OL,7,Fconsidered the case very carefully, we
OL,8,Fhave decided not to revisit the
OL,9,Fproposal to cease named single and
OL,10,Fjoint honours degrees in ancient
OL,11,Fhistory, and religion and theology. I
OL,12,Fdo understand that this will be very
OL,13,Fdisappointing news for all academics
OL,14,Fwho are deeply committed to these
OL,15,Fdisciplines.
